  m_text: "<size=120%><b>Welcome to <color=#8B4513>Lumber Tycoon!</color></b></size>\n\n<size=80%><i>Your
    journey to becoming a forest mogul starts here.</i></size>\n\n<align=left><b><color=#D2691E>\u2022
    Step 1:</color></b> Find an <b>Oak Tree</b> and start harvesting.\n<b><color=#D2691E>\u2022
    Step 2:</color></b> Collect enough wood to unlock <b>Maple</b>.\n<b><color=#D2691E>\u2022
    Step 3:</color></b> Build generators to automate your empire!</align>\n\n<size=90%><color=#32CD32><b>GOOD
